{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_02_01",
  "title": "ハッピーニューイヤー2301",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あけまして\nおめでとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昨年は\n大変お世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your great\nsupport last year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "本年もよろしく\nお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's work together well\nagain this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "と言っても年末から\nお仕事続きだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although saying that‚ we've\nbeen working since\nthe end of last year‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり年が明けた感じも\nしないけれどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so it doesn't really feel like\nthe year has started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですね\nクリスマスに大晦日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Christmas‚\nNew Year's Eve‚ and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "この後はお正月の特番に\n出演ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "then we have a shooting\nfor New Year's specials.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お仕事がいただけるのはいい\nことですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's good that\nwe're getting work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん\n無理は禁物ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚\noverworking is not good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そう言う瑠依が一番\n無理をしそうだけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ Rui-chan‚ it feels like\n you're the one most likely\nto overwork.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "莉央さんが言うのも\n不思議な感じがしますけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's weird to hear you say\nthat though‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの練習はハード\nだって聞いてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've heard that LizNoir's\npractice is quite intense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5333333969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あはは\nそう言う琴乃ちゃんも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ Kotono-chan‚\nyou're also as",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央ちゃんと同じくらい\nストイックだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "hardworking as Rio-san‚\nright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だ、だって、莉央さんも\n瑠依さんもさくらも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I know Rio-san‚\nRui-chan‚ and Sakura-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな頑張ってるから。私も\n負けてられないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "are all working so hard‚ so\nI can't afford to lose either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ、今年も、お互いに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ this year‚\nlet's continue to inspire",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "刺激し合って\n成長していきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and grow together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうね、スケジュールは\n無理のないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ {user}-san\nwill make sure the",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666662216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが\n調整してくれるでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "schedule is manageable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Please continue\nto watch over",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3999995549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "今年も私達のこと、そばで\n見守っていて下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "us closely this year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、改めて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ once again‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_02_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ハッピーニューイヤー！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}